org.extremecomponents.table.bean
Class ColumnDefaults

java.lang.Object
  org.extremecomponents.table.bean.ColumnDefaults
final class ColumnDefaults
extends Object

Pull all the default values for the ColumnTag. Because the default values could be coming from the properties or resource bundle this class will abstract that out.

Author:
Jeff Johnston
